high_descs: Move to the sink to the left of the second sink
Get a bar of soap from the cabinet and close the door
Move to the tub to the right of you
Put the soap in the tub
Move to the left side of the tub
Pick up a bar of soap from the tub
Move to the center of the tub
Put the soap in the tub
anns.task_desc: Put two bars of soap in the tub.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the cabinets below the sink on the left.
Open the left cabinet below the sink and pick up the pink bar of soap from the left cabinet.
Turn right and walk to the tub.
Place the soap in the tub.
Turn left and walk to the soap on the edge of the tub.
Pick up the soap on the edge of the tub.
Turn right and walk to the soap in the tub.
Place the soap to the left of the other bar of soap in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Place two bars of soap in the tub.

high_descs: turn right and face the sink
open the left most cabinet under the sink, and remove a pink soap bar
turn to the right and walk over to the bath tub with the pink soap
put the pink soap in the bottom of the bath tub
turn and look to the left and turn right to face the bath tub again
pick up the pink bar of soap on the edge of the bath tub
turn right, take a step back, and turn left to face the tub again
put the bar of soap in the bath tub bottom to the left of the other bar of soap
anns.task_desc: put two bars of pink soap on the bottom of the bath tub
